A quick tip: Try to help the submeters to save some time by modifying the segment submission time. For example:

segmentStart = segmentStart - 1 Second or two;
segmantEnd = segmantEnd -  1 Second or two;

This applies for any unrealted things in the video for the sake of time consumption while submeting.

Overall, excellent work and you have my deepest respect for doing such a useful tool.

~Peter
